~ character_1
1: The abyss listens before it answers. Carry this echo with care.
=> END

~ character_2
1: Some threads remember the shape of light, even down here.
=> END

~ character_3
1: The deeper path opens only for those who gather what remains.
=> END

~ character_4
1: A small pulse returns to you. The silence is not empty.
=> END

~ character_5
1: A small pulse returns to you. You are scared
=> END
